quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  95,1,"By the fig (or the place Tiin where Noah’s ship embarked), and the olive (or Zaita in Jerusalam, were Jesus received and preached the message of God)"
  95,2,and Mount Sinai (where Moses received the message of God)
  95,3,"and this city of security (Mecca, where our prophet Muhammad initially received and preached the message of God, all these are witnesses that)"
  95,4,We had indeed created man in the best form
  95,5,then We brought him back as the lowest of those who are low
  95,6,"except those who believed and did righteous works, then for them there is an unfailing reward"
  95,7,Then after this what makes you deny the judgment
  95,8,"Is not God the Best Judge, of all the judges"